'''Tyu''' was a [[Crime lord/Legends|crime lord]] whose base of operations was on [[Kazlin 5]].

For a time, Tyu employed the [[Rodian/Legends|Rodian]] [[Dheendo]] as one of his [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunters]], but Dheendo decided that bounty hunting was not for him, and left Tyu's employment to join the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]].

